object Tpch9 {
  import Helper._
  val precision = 7; // significative numbers (7 to pass r_sumdivgrp, 10 otherwise)
  val diff_p = Math.pow(0.1,precision)
  
  def execute(args:Array[String],f:List[Any]=>Unit) = bench(args,(d:String,p:Int,t:Long,b:Int)=>run[Tpch9](Seq(
    (new java.io.FileInputStream("/Users/dashti/Documents/MyWorkspaces/DATASRC/dbtoaster/experiments/data/tpch/"+d+"/lineitem.csv"),new Adaptor.CSV("LINEITEM","long,long,long,long,double,double,double,double,string,string,date,date,date,string,string,string","\\Q|\\E",if(d.endsWith("_del")) "ins+del" else "insert"),Split()),
    (new java.io.FileInputStream("/Users/dashti/Documents/MyWorkspaces/DATASRC/dbtoaster/experiments/data/tpch/"+d+"/orders.csv"),new Adaptor.CSV("ORDERS","long,long,string,double,date,string,string,long,string","\\Q|\\E",if(d.endsWith("_del")) "ins+del" else "insert"),Split()),
    (new java.io.FileInputStream("/Users/dashti/Documents/MyWorkspaces/DATASRC/dbtoaster/experiments/data/tpch/"+d+"/part.csv"),new Adaptor.CSV("PART","long,string,string,string,string,long,string,double,string","\\Q|\\E",if(d.endsWith("_del")) "ins+del" else "insert"),Split()),

  ),p,t,b),f)
